Class Controller_Images

java.lang.Object
  images.Abstract_Image
      images.Controller_Images

public class Controller_Images
extends Abstract_Image

This class contains all of the images for the controller panel Allows only one class to be imported and for easy manipulation of the images The variables here are static so you don't need to create the object
